items.title: S&P, Dow Pharma Stocks Boomerang On Drug-Pricing Order That Is 'All Bark' And 'Little Bite'
items.description: Pharmaceutical stocks boomeranged Monday after Trump signed an executive order tying drug prices in the U.S. to international price tags.
